column5: Just wondering if anyone knows if the steelies are still bitin' in the Niagara? If so, any suggestions as to where?
The way we do it is, You go see, and then tell us how you made out.  Skunk reports are ok too, maybe I learn more from them than the 'Sleighed Em' reports.  The puns are downhill from here on.
Thank you Sir, may I have another...!!!! I like the humour on here already..  Thanks
